\f1\b0\fs46 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1/2 (3 pounds) large watermelon, peeled and cut into 1-inch chunks\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/4 cup sugar\
{\listtext	\'95	}3/4 cup watermelon flavored 70 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/proof/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 proof}} vodka (recommended: Smirnoff Twist of {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/watermelon/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Watermelon}})* see Cook's Note\
